@startuml
title BP-21 - Parent Views Multi Student Outstanding Bills

skinparam shadowing false
skinparam activity {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
  DiamondBackgroundColor White
  DiamondBorderColor Black
}
skinparam note {
  BackgroundColor White
  BorderColor Black
}

|Parent Guardian|
start
:Login to parent workspace;
:Select school tenant if multiple;
:Open children or outstanding bill page;

|Platform|
:Read UserID, TenantID and RoleCode from JWT;
:Load students linked to parent in tenant;

if (Student requested explicitly?) then (Yes)
  :Validate parent owns requested student;
else (No)
  :Use all linked students in tenant;
endif

:Find obligations with outstanding amount greater than zero;
:Calculate paid amount and remaining amount;
:Return outstanding bill list;

|Parent Guardian|
:Review bills for each child;
stop

note right
Current endpoint:
GET /students/{studentId}/outstanding
Tenant and parent ownership validation are mandatory.
end note
@enduml
